=======
License
=======

The ``la`` package is distributed under a Simplified BSD license. Parts of
NumPy, Scipy and numpydoc, which all have BSD licenses, are included in ``la``.
Parts of Matplotlib, which has Python Software Foundation like license, are
inlcuded in ``la``.

*Numpy*

- la/deflarry.py(astype, take): Docstrings
- la/flarry.py(rand, randn, unique): Docstrings

*Scipy*

- la/external/scipy.py: Functions and docstrings

*numpydoc*

- la/doc/shinxext/: Entire directory                

*matplotlib*

- la/external/matplotlib.py


